235
00:23:27,354 --> 00:23:30,721
Yeah, Miss Garber!
You'll put Eric in all your plays!

236
00:23:30,924 --> 00:23:33,586
Eric, I'll put you in all my plays!

237
00:23:33,861 --> 00:23:37,763
