three weeks to memorize all this?

238
00:23:37,965 --> 00:23:42,459
You couldn't pull this off
in three months! De Niro couldn't!

239
00:23:42,670 --> 00:23:44,262
I didn't write it, okay?

240
00:23:44,471 --> 00:23:49,067
